&lt;li&gt;Lead compensation cycles (merit, equity refresh, promotions), including modeling, calibration, and manager communications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct regular market benchmarking using Radford or comparable surveys; maintain salary bands and refresh annually&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Talent Acquisition on offer strategy, competitive positioning, and real-time compensation intelligence&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Equity Compensation&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Legal and Finance on equity mechanics, liquidity events, and board materials; build education resources that help employees understand and value their ownership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
